They were horrible One of the worst experiences Ive had at a store in Korea in 17 years here Picture this I leave my kids at home alone at 1030am 11 and 8 to quickly get an ice cream cake for their friends birthday expecting it to take maybe 10 mins I get there and try to buy a cake When I open the fridge door its sealed a little tight so I pull justa little harderthe handle pops off Sorry I hand the handle to the cashier pay for my cake and expect to leave But the workers are like Wait a minute We have to call the owner The owner instructs them to make me wait there no doubt in an attempt to try and get money out of me to pay for their faulty door I wait for 20 mins or so getting angrier by the minute I decided to record a couple vids of the incident My phone battery dies of course Completely fed up I told the workers to call the police The police came took my information and let me leaveAT 1130 Ive since complained to the main headquarters in Korea via my wife and nothing Not even an apology Never buying anything here again
